project_descr: Increase Political Participation of Women in Samoa (IPPWS) Phase II builds on the successful achievements from Phase I and to support efforts to mobilize resources for its implementation.

outputs.output_descr: The initiation phase focuses on undertaking comprehensive consultations in country; building durable partnerships, including building on the joint partnership with UN Women from Phase I, to take into the implementation phase.

document_name: Incresing the Political Participation of Women in Samoa (IPPWS) Phase II
project_title: increase political participation of women in samoa
